\li2 Atupale hanea avona vakayeka 1 Kolini 7:21,22 ago.
\li1 1 Pita 5:13
\li2 Papilonia kumafena PitaꞋa huno hiana Lomu veafe avame ke huno Papilonia kumale huno hu-maine. PitaꞋma mainea kanafina Lomu veaꞋmoꞋya nayoma Papilonia veaꞋmoꞋyama hu-mainaya augafa kava huꞋya kefo yana maiꞋya hageno hu-maine.
\li1 Leveleseni 2:10
\li2 TeniꞋa (10) kanaema huno hu-maineana avame ke hu-maine. Aupa kanafi Anumayamoma amakuꞋa aminaya veala kame lagiꞋya kae-mategahae huno nehunofe teniꞋa (10) kanae huno hu-maine.
\li1 Leveleseni 8:3
\li2 Atupale hanea avona vakayeka Matiu 23:18 ago.
\li1 Leveleseni 11:1-2
\li2 Anumaya Kotina mono nomaꞋaema hiana Yisasina amakuꞋa amitafa hu-mainaya veafe avame kea hu-maleno hu-maine. Yisasi kema nohaviya veaꞋmoꞋya malaga maineꞋya Yisasina amakuꞋama amitafa hu-mainaya veaꞋnea kame hu-mategahe nehae.
\li1 Leveleseni 13:11
\li2 Nagola alu afai afuema hiana havige huno aunema laga nehia kanohe hu-maine. Na avona vakayeka eteka Leveleseni 16:13 hapalika havio.
\li1 Leveleseni 14:1
\li2 Atupale hanea avona vakayeka Lomu 9:33 ago.
\li1 Leveleseni 16:13
\li2 Anima havigeꞋyama nehia aune kanohena alu afai afuma huꞋya haya kanohe hu-maine. Na avona vakayeka eteka Lev.13:11 hapalika havio.
\li1 Leveleseni 16:19
\li2 NagoꞋa Anumayamona amakuꞋama aminaya veaꞋmoꞋya maꞋa amakesa havimainae. “Papilonia kumaꞋmoꞋa Lomu koꞋmo ame kana hu-maine.” huꞋya hu-mainae. PitaꞋa mani kea avame ke huno Lomu veafe Papilonia veaꞋne huno hu-maine. Na avona vakayeka eteka 1 Pita 5:13 hapalika havio. NagoꞋa veala Papilonia mukiꞋa alu kote alu kotega KalaisiꞋene agai kema nehaviya veaꞋnene kamea hu neꞋamataya veaꞋne mainae huꞋya hu-mainae. HaenagaꞋa Anumaya KotiꞋa aniꞋama nehaya veala alino haviya hu-mategahie. Na avona vakayeka eteka Lev.17 ene 18 ene hapalika havio. EtenoꞋma esiana agaila amakuꞋama aminesaya veaꞋneꞋage me mavaleno visiaꞋamo kanaleꞋya huꞋya ofalisaya kumatela haiꞋya KalaisiꞋene nagopi mo lokaeꞋya agola maige maige huꞋya maigahae.
\li1 Leveleseni 17:2
\li2 VeaꞋmoꞋya kumaima nehae huꞋyama hayana Anumayamona akave omaleꞋya ma mopafi yafekeꞋya haviꞋya akave nemalaya yafe hu-maine. Anumaya Koti kema atalenaya yamoꞋa maꞋa hu-maine aꞋneꞋamima amataleꞋya ute ete hayaꞋamoꞋya kumai aꞋnema amavayu nehaya avamete kava hu-maine huno hu-maine.
\li1 Leveleseni 19:7
\li2 Sipi sipi nafaꞋnema hiana Kalaisife hu-maine. A aligahie hunoꞋma hu-maineana ani aꞋnea mukiꞋa Yisasina amakuꞋama amitafa hu-mainaya veafe hu-maine. HaenagaꞋa KalaisiꞋma esia kanafina amakaya ve alave huꞋya maigahae huno hu-maine. 
